data.description: Welcome to the pinnacle of luxurious living in the esteemed Fox Meadow subdivision of Hope Mills! This stunning two-story residence offers a wealth of features that will leave you speechless. With 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there is a ton of space! The open layout and built-in shelving in the great room create a sense of grandeur and elegance. Prepare to be enchanted by the ceramic tile flooring and the expansive master bedroom that exudes tranquility. Double vanities in both bathrooms add a touch of luxury, while the large pantry and walk-in closets provide ample storage. The recent replacement of one HVAC unit ensures optimal comfort. Step outside and you'll find a front porch, a spacious rear deck, and a sprawling backyard. The sizable fifth bedroom presents an ideal layout for a bonus room. This home is the epitome of style, sophistication, and comfort–a true dream come true.
